    <item>
      <title>美国银行看好盈利前景，新任首席执行官上任，Peloton 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/peloton-gains-as-bofa-turns-bullish-on-profit-outlook-new-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司周一将这家健身公司的评级上调两级，称赞其盈利前景和对新任首席执行官的积极看法，因此 Peloton Interactive Inc. 获得了罕见的买入评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/peloton-gains-as-bofa-turns-bullish-on-profit-outlook-new-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:14:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>B. Riley 董事长因 FRG 破产而“个人患病”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/b-riley-chairman-feels-personally-sick-as-frg-goes-bankrupt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资公司 B. Riley Financial Inc. 的联合创始人布莱恩特·莱利 (Bryant Riley) 告诉员工，Franchise Group Inc. 倒闭后他“个人感到非常难过”。而就在一年多前，他曾协助安排了一笔价值 28 亿美元的收购，并使其成为该公司的主要持股之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/b-riley-chairman-feels-personally-sick-as-frg-goes-bankrupt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:24:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构拒绝核协议后美国电力股暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/us-power-stocks-slump-after-regulator-rejects-nuclear-agreement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国最高能源监管机构拒绝 Talen 的数据中心供电计划后，Talen Energy Corp. 和其他美国电力公司的股价周一暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/us-power-stocks-slump-after-regulator-rejects-nuclear-agreement</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 13:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行希望释放资本以抵御意大利联合信贷银行的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/commerzbank-ceo-looks-to-free-up-capital-to-fend-off-unicredit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行首席执行官 Bettina Orlopp 正在寻求释放更多资本用于支付或投资，面对竞争对手 UniCredit SpA 的潜在收购，她主张成为一家独立银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/commerzbank-ceo-looks-to-free-up-capital-to-fend-off-unicredit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 13:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“特朗普贸易”疑虑拖累美元，提振美国国债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/dollar-falls-bond-futures-gain-as-some-trump-trades-are-pared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者减少对共和党人唐纳德·特朗普在周二美国大选中获胜的押注，美国国债收益率大幅下跌，美元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/dollar-falls-bond-futures-gain-as-some-trump-trades-are-pared</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 01:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：选举“势均力敌” 标普 500 指数摇摆不定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市挣扎寻找方向，债券上涨，美元下跌，在联邦储备委员会作出决定之前，民意调查继续显示美国总统大选竞争激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 22:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员削减风险敞口后，选举焦虑笼罩新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/election-anxiety-grips-emerging-markets-as-investors-slash-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从墨西哥城到上海，经历了动荡之年的贸易商们正准备迎接新的政治冲击：美国总统大选有可能颠覆全球贸易，并可能扰乱发展中国家的经济前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/election-anxiety-grips-emerging-markets-as-investors-slash-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
